  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "[Control theory](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Control_theory) is a branch of applied mathematics that deals with the design of control policies for actuated dynamical systems. Control engineering is a cross-discipline field that applies control theory to a wide range of systems such as industrial plants, aerospace, robotics and more.",
